description: The council of Tilloy-lez-Marchiennes chose Marie Cau as their new mayor on Saturday.
title: Marie Cau: First transgender mayor elected in France
title_page: Marie Cau: First transgender mayor elected in France - BBC News
maintext: They elected all the councillors from the "Deciding Together" list, among them Ms Cau. On Saturday these councillors voted nearly unanimously to make her the new mayor of the town.
